JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Warehouse
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause: whse,name,addr[1],addr[2],city,state,zipcd,phoneno
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: pub.icsd
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause: cono = {IntegrationConnector_SXeCompany}

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Services
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause: codeval,descrip
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: pub.sasta
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause: cono = {IntegrationConnector_SXeCompany} and codeiden = 'S'

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Carriers
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause: codeval,descrip
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: pub.sasta
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause: cono = {IntegrationConnector_SXeCompany} and codeiden = 'S'

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Payment Methods
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause: codeval, descrip, curdate() as ActivateOn
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: pub.sasta
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause:
cono = {IntegrationConnector_SXeCompany} and
codeiden = 'T'

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Addon Amounts
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause:
pub.oeeh oeeh 
left join pub.addon addon1 on addon1.cono = oeeh.cono and addon1.ordertype = 'oe' and addon1.orderno = oeeh.orderno and addon1.ordersuf = oeeh.ordersuf and addon1.addonno = '02' 
left join pub.addon addon2 on addon2.cono = oeeh.cono and addon2.ordertype = 'oe' and addon2.orderno = oeeh.orderno and addon2.ordersuf = oeeh.ordersuf and addon2.addonno <> '02'
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause:
oeeh.cono = {IntegrationConnector_SXeCompany} 
and oeeh.orderno > {IntegrationConnector_SXeStartingOrderNumber}
and oeeh.transtype not in ('BL','QU','ST','FO','BR')
and oeeh.stagecd <> 0 and oeeh.stagecd <> 9 
and oeeh.enterdt is not null
and oeeh.transdt > curdate() - 5
group by oeeh.cono, oeeh.orderno, oeeh.ordersuf, oeeh.transtype, oeeh.taxamt

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Order Lines
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
convert('varchar',oeeh.orderno) || '-' || lpad(convert('varchar',oeeh.ordersuf), 2, '0')  AS ErpOrderNumber,
oeel.lineno as lineno,
0 as releaseno,
oeel.custno as custno,
oeel.shipprod as shipprod,
case oeel.specnstype 
when 'n' then (oeel.proddesc || ' ' || oeel.proddesc2) 
else rtrim(replace(icsp.descrip, ';', ' ')) 
end as descrip,
oeel.qtyord * (case oeel.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) as qtyord,
oeel.stkqtyord * (case oeel.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) as stkqtyord,
oeel.whse as whse,
oeel.unit as unit,
case oeeh.stagecd when 0 then 0.0 when 1 then 0.0 else oeel.qtyship * (case oeel.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) end as QtyShipped,
case oeeh.stagecd when 0 then 0.0 when 1 then 0.0 else oeel.stkqtyship * (case oeel.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) end as StockQtyShipped,
oeel.price as price, 
case oeeh.stagecd when 0 then oeel.netord when 1 then oeel.netord else oeel.netamt end * (case oeel.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) as LineTotal,
oeeh.shipdt as shipdt,
rtrim(replace(ifnull(com.noteln, ''), ';', ' ')) as noteln,
oeel.unit as unit,
oeeh.custno as custno,
oeeh.shipto as shipto,
oeel.promisedt as promisedt,
oeel.statustype as statustype,
oeel.specnstype as specnstype,
case
when oeel.qtyship < oeel.qtyord and oeel.reqshipdt <= curdate() and oeeh.stagecd = '1' then 'True'
else 'False'
end as backordered
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause:
pub.oeeh oeeh
inner join pub.oeel oeel on oeeh.cono = oeel.cono and oeeh.orderno = oeel.orderno and oeeh.ordersuf = oeel.ordersuf
left join pub.icsp icsp on icsp.cono = oeel.cono and icsp.prod = oeel.shipprod
left join pub.com on oeel.cono = com.cono and com.comtype = 'oe' and oeel.orderno = com.orderno and oeel.ordersuf = com.ordersuf and oeel.lineno = com.lineno and (com.printfl = 1 OR com.printfl2 = 1)

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Order Header
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
convert('varchar',oeeh.orderno) || '-' || lpad(convert('varchar',oeeh.ordersuf), 2, '0')  AS ErpOrderNumber,
oeeh.stagecd as status,
case oeeh.transtype
when 'SO' then convert('varchar','Sales Order')
when 'BR' then convert('varchar','Blanket Release')
when 'DO' then convert('varchar','Direct Ship Order')
when 'CS' then convert('varchar','Counter Sales Order')
when 'RM' then convert('varchar','Return Material Order')
when 'ST' then convert('varchar','Standing Order')
when 'QU' then convert('varchar','Quote')
when 'BL' then convert('varchar','Blanket Order')
when 'FO' then convert('varchar','Future Order')
end as ordertype,
oeeh.enterdt as OrderDate,
oeeh.canceldt as canceldt,
oeeh.custpo as custpo,
oeeh.custno as custno,
oeeh.shipto as shipto,
oeeh.termstype as termstype,
oeeh.shipviaty as shipviaty,
oeeh.reqshipdt as reqshipdt,
oeeh.slsrepout as slsrepout,
oeeh.slsrepin as slsrepin,
arsc.name as name,
ifnull(left(convert('varchar', arsc.addr), locate(';', convert('varchar', arsc.addr)) - 1), '') as addr1,
ifnull(right(convert('varchar', arsc.addr) , length(arsc.addr) - locate(';', convert('varchar', arsc.addr))), '') as addr2,
arsc.city as city,
arsc.state as state,
arsc.zipcd as zipcd,
arsc.countrycd as countrycd,
oeeh.shiptonm as shiptonm,
ifnull(left(convert('varchar', oeeh.shiptoaddr), locate(';', convert('varchar', oeeh.shiptoaddr)) - 1), '') as shiptoaddr1,
ifnull(right(convert('varchar', oeeh.shiptoaddr) , length(oeeh.shiptoaddr) - locate(';', convert('varchar', oeeh.shiptoaddr))), '') as shiptoaddr2,
oeeh.shiptocity as shiptocity,
oeeh.shiptost as shiptost,
oeeh.shiptozip as shiptozip,
oeeh.countrycd as shiptocountry,
case oeeh.stagecd
when '0' then oeeh.totlineord * (case oeeh.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end)
when '1' then oeeh.totlineord * (case oeeh.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end)
else oeeh.totlineamt * (case oeeh.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end)
end as ProductTotal,
oeeh.specdiscamt * (case oeeh.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) as specdiscamt,
case oeeh.stagecd
when '0' then oeeh.totinvord
when '1' then oeeh.totinvord 
else oeeh.totinvamt
end * (case oeeh.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) as OrderTotal,
rtrim(replace(ifnull(notes.noteln,''), ';', ' ')) as notesln,
oeeh.currencyty as currencyty,
oeeh.shipdt as shipdt
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause:
pub.oeeh oeeh join
pub.arsc arsc on arsc.cono = oeeh.cono and arsc.custno = oeeh.custno
left join pub.notes notes on notes.cono = oeeh.cono and notes.notestype = 'o' and notes.primarykey = oeeh.orderno and (notes.secondarykey = '' or notes.secondarykey = oeeh.ordersuf) and (notes.printfl2 = 1 or notes.printfl5 = 1)

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Cross Sells
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
icsec.prod as SxProd,
icsec.altprod as RelatedProd,
'ProductRelationship' as ListType,
'CrossSell' as ListValue
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause:
pub.icsec icsec join
pub.icsp icsp on icsp.cono = icsec.cono and icsp.prod = icsec.prod join
pub.icsp icsp2 on icsp2.cono = icsec.cono and icsp2.prod = icsec.altprod
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause:
icsec.cono = {IntegrationConnector_SXeCompany} and
icsec.rectype = 'O' and
icsp.statustype = 'A' and icsp.prodtype = 'S' and
icsp2.statustype = 'A' and icsp2.prodtype = 'S'

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Customer/Product
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
icsec.custno as custno,
'' as shipto,
icsec.altprod as SxProd,
icsec.prod as CustomerProd,
icsec.unitsell as unitsell
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause:
pub.icsec icsec join
pub.arsc arsc on arsc.cono = icsec.cono and arsc.custno = icsec.custno join
pub.icsp icsp on icsp.cono = icsec.cono and icsp.prod = icsec.altprod
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause:
icsec.cono = {IntegrationConnector_SXeCompany}
and icsec.rectype = 'C'
and icsec.shipto = ''
and icsp.statustype = 'A'
and icsp.prodtype = 'S'
and arsc.statustype = 1

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Invoice Lines
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
convert('varchar',oeeh.orderno) || '-' || lpad(convert('varchar',oeeh.ordersuf), 2, '0')  AS InvoiceNumber,
oeel.lineno as lineno,
0 as releaseno,
oeel.shipprod as shipprod,
case oeel.specnstype 
when 'n' then (oeel.proddesc || ' ' || oeel.proddesc2) 
else rtrim(replace(icsp.descrip, ';', ' ')) 
end as descrip,
oeel.qtyord * (case oeel.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) as qtyord,
oeel.stkqtyord * (case oeel.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) as stkqtyord,
oeel.whse as whse,
oeel.unit as unit,
oeel.qtyship * (case oeel.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) as QtyShipped,
oeel.stkqtyship * (case oeel.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) as StockQtyShipped,
oeel.price as price, 
oeel.netamt * (case oeel.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) as LineTotal,
oeeh.shipdt as shipdt,
oeel.unit as unit,
oeeh.custno as custno,
oeeh.shipto as shipto,
oeel.promisedt as promisedt,
oeel.statustype as statustype,
oeel.specnstype as specnstype
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause:
pub.oeeh oeeh
inner join pub.oeel oeel on oeel.cono = oeeh.cono and oeel.orderno = oeeh.orderno and oeel.ordersuf = oeeh.ordersuf
left join pub.icsp icsp on icsp.cono = oeel.cono and icsp.prod = oeel.shipprod

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Invoice Header
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
convert('varchar',oeeh.orderno) || '-' || lpad(convert('varchar',oeeh.ordersuf), 2, '0')  AS InvoiceNumber,
case
when oeeh.stagecd = '4' then convert('varchar','Invoiced')
when oeeh.stagecd = '5' then convert('varchar','Paid')
end as status,
case
when oeeh.stagecd = '4' then 1
when oeeh.stagecd = '5' then 0
end as IsOpen,
case
when oeeh.stagecd = '4' then TotInvAmt -
ifnull((select sum(aret.amount) from pub.aret aret where aret.cono = oeeh.cono and
aret.invno = oeeh.orderno and aret.invsuf = oeeh.invsuf and aret.invdt = oeeh.invoicedt and aret.statustype = 0 and aret.transcd = 11),0) * (case oeeh.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end)  
when oeeh.stagecd = '5' then 0
end as InvoiceBalance,
ifnull(aret.duedt, oeeh.invoicedt) as DueDate,
case oeeh.transtype
when 'SO' then convert('varchar','Sales Order')
when 'BR' then convert('varchar','Blanket Release')
when 'DO' then convert('varchar','Direct Ship Order')
when 'CS' then convert('varchar','Counter Sales Order')
when 'RM' then convert('varchar','Return Material Order')
when 'ST' then convert('varchar','Standing Order')
when 'QU' then convert('varchar','Quote')
when 'BL' then convert('varchar','Blanket Order')
when 'FO' then convert('varchar','Future Order')
end as ordertype,
oeeh.enterdt as OrderDate,
oeeh.invoicedt as InvoiceDate,
oeeh.custno as custno,
oeeh.custpo as custpo,
oeeh.shipto as shipto,
oeeh.termstype as termstype,
oeeh.shipviaty as shipviaty,
oeeh.slsrepout as slsrepout,
oeeh.slsrepin as slsrepin,
arsc.name as name,
ifnull(left(convert('varchar', arsc.addr), locate(';', convert('varchar', arsc.addr)) - 1), '') as addr1,
ifnull(right(convert('varchar', arsc.addr) , length(arsc.addr) - locate(';', convert('varchar', arsc.addr))), '') as addr2,
arsc.city as city,
arsc.state as state,
arsc.zipcd as zipcd,
arsc.countrycd as countrycd,
oeeh.shiptonm as shiptonm,
ifnull(left(convert('varchar', oeeh.shiptoaddr), locate(';', convert('varchar', oeeh.shiptoaddr)) - 1), '') as shiptoaddr1,
ifnull(right(convert('varchar', oeeh.shiptoaddr) , length(oeeh.shiptoaddr) - locate(';', convert('varchar', oeeh.shiptoaddr))), '') as shiptoaddr2,
oeeh.shiptocity as shiptocity,
oeeh.shiptost as shiptost,
oeeh.shiptozip as shiptozip,
oeeh.countrycd as shiptocountry,
oeeh.totlineamt * (case oeeh.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) as ProductTotal,
oeeh.specdiscamt * (case oeeh.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) as specdiscamt,
oeeh.totinvamt * (case oeeh.transtype when 'rm' then -1 else 1 end) as InvoiceTotal,
oeeh.currencyty as currencyty,
oeeh.shipdt as shipdt
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause:
pub.oeeh oeeh join
pub.arsc arsc on arsc.cono = oeeh.cono and arsc.custno = oeeh.custno left join
pub.aret aret on aret.cono = oeeh.cono and aret.custno = oeeh.custno and aret.invdt = oeeh.invoicedt and aret.invno = oeeh.orderno and aret.invsuf = oeeh.ordersuf and aret.transcd = 0

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Invoice Addons
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause:
pub.oeeh oeeh 
left join pub.addon addon1 on addon1.cono = oeeh.cono and addon1.ordertype = 'oe' and addon1.orderno = oeeh.orderno and addon1.ordersuf = oeeh.ordersuf and addon1.addonno = '02' 
left join pub.addon addon2 on addon2.cono = oeeh.cono and addon2.ordertype = 'oe' and addon2.orderno = oeeh.orderno and addon2.ordersuf = oeeh.ordersuf and addon2.addonno <> '02'

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Product and Catalog
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
icsp.prod as erpnumber,
icsp.descrip[1] + ' ' + icsp.descrip[2] as descrip,
icsp.descrip[1]+ ' ' + icsp.descrip[2] + ' ' + icsp.prod as URLSegment,
NULLIF(1,1) as DeactivateOn,
icsp.unitstock as unitstock,
icsp.sellmult as sellmult,
CASE WHEN icsp.sellmult <> 0 then 'Multiple Only' else '' END as RoundingRule,
1 as TrackInventory,
ifnull(convert('varchar',icsw.listprice),'0') as listprice,
ifnull(convert('varchar',icsw.pricetype),'0') as pricetype,
icsp.prodcat as prodcat,
ifnull(icsw.prodline,'') as prodline,
ifnull(icsw.vendprod,'') as ManufacturerItem,
icsp.weight as weight,
icsp.length as length,
icsp.width as width,
icsp.height as height
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause:
pub.icsp icsp 
left join pub.icsw icsw on icsw.prod = icsp.prod and icsw.cono = icsp.cono and icsw.whse = {IntegrationConnector_SXeRefreshWarehouse}
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause:
icsp.cono = {IntegrationConnector_SXeCompany} and
icsp.prodtype = 'S' and icsp.statustype = 'A'
-- NOTE - REMOVE THIS SECTION IF YOU DO NOT WANT THE CATALOG
UNION SELECT
icsc.catalog as erpnumber,
icsc.descrip[1] + ' ' + icsc.descrip[2] as descrip,
icsc.descrip[1]+ ' ' + icsc.descrip[2] + ' ' + icsc.catalog as URLSegment,
NULLIF(1,1) as DeactivateOn,
icsc.unitstock as unitstock,
0 as sellmult,
'' as RoundingRule,
0 as TrackInventory,
ifnull(convert('varchar',icsc.listprice),'0') as listprice,
ifnull(convert('varchar',icsc.pricetype),'0') as pricetype,
icsc.prodcat as prodcat,
ifnull(icsc.prodline,'') as prodline,
ifnull(icsc.vendprod,'') as ManufacturerItem,
icsc.weight as weight,
icsc.length as length,
icsc.width as width,
icsc.height as height
from pub.icsc 
where statustype = 'A' and
not exists (select 1 from pub.icsp where prod = catalog) and
-- NOTE: This is intentional to not inadvertently include catalog entries
icsc.catalog like '<catalog mask>'

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Product Units of Measure
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
icseu.prod as prod,
icseu.units as units,
ifnull(sasta.descrip,icseu.descrip) as descrip,
icseu.unitconv as unitconv,
case when icsp.unitsell = icseu.units
    then 1 else 0
    end as isdefault
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause:
pub.icseu as icseu
inner join pub.icsp icsp on icseu.prod = icsp.prod and icseu.cono = icsp.cono
left join pub.sasta on icseu.units = sasta.codeval and sasta.codeiden = 'u' and sasta.cono = icsp.cono
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause:
icsp.cono = {IntegrationConnector_SXeCompany} and 
icsp.prodtype = 'S'  and
icsp.statustype = 'A'

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Shipment Package
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
convert('varchar',oeehp.orderno) || '-' || lpad(convert('varchar',oeehp.ordersuf), 2, '0')  AS Shipment,
oeehp.freightamt as freightamt, 
oeehp.pkgno as pkgno,
oeehp.shipviaty as shipviaty,
oeehp.trackerno as trackerno
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: pub.oeehp oeehp

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Shipment Header
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
convert('varchar',oeehp.orderno) || '-' || lpad(convert('varchar',oeehp.ordersuf), 2, '0')  AS ErpOrderNumber,
convert('varchar',oeehp.orderno) || '-' || lpad(convert('varchar',oeehp.ordersuf), 2, '0')  AS Shipment,
oeehp.transdt as ShipmentDate
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: pub.oeehp oeehp

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Inventory
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause: icsw.Prod,whse, qtyonhand - qtyreservd - qtycommit as QtyAvailable,avgcost
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause:
pub.icsw icsw join
pub.icsp icsp on icsp.cono = icsw.cono and icsp.prod = icsw.prod
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause:
icsw.cono = {IntegrationConnector_SXeCompany} and icsp.prodtype = 'S' and icsp.statustype = 'A'
and icsw.qtyonhand - icsw.qtyreservd - icsw.qtycommit > 0

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Salesperson
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause: slsrep, name, email, slstitle, phoneno, mgr
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: pub.smsn
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause: cono = {IntegrationConnector_SXeCompany}

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: BillTo Customers
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
arsc.custno as custno,
'' as shipto,
arsc.custtype as custtype,
arsc.name as name,
arsc.email as email,
arsc.phoneno as phoneno,
arsc.faxphoneno as faxphoneno,
arsc.termstype as termstype,
arsc.pricetype  as pricetype,
arsc.currencyty as currencyty,
arsc.whse as whse,
arsc.slsrepout as slsrepout,
arsc.slsrepin as slsrepin,
ifnull(left(convert('varchar', arsc.addr), locate(';', convert('varchar', arsc.addr)) - 1), '') as addr1,
ifnull(right(convert('varchar', arsc.addr) , length(arsc.addr) - locate(';', convert('varchar', arsc.addr))), '') as addr2,
'' as addr3,
arsc.city as city,
arsc.state as state,
case when arsc.countrycd = '' then 'US' when arsc.countrycd != '' then arsc.countrycd end as countrycd,
arsc.zipcd as zipcd,     
arsc.shipviaty as shipviaty,
case when arsc.pdcustno = 0 then '' when arsc.pdcustno != 0 then convert('varchar', arsc.pdcustno) end as pdcustno,
'' as pdshipto,
arsc.bankno as bankno,
case when arsc.pricecd = '' then '' 
         when arsc.pricecd != '' then convert('varchar',arsc.pricecd) end as pricecd,
convert('varchar',arsc.disccd) as disccd,
arsc.credlim as credlim,
arsc.statustype as statustype,
case when convert('integer',arsc.shipreqfl) = 0 then 'true' else 'false' end  as shipreqfl,
arsc.poreqfl as porequired,
case when arsc.selltype <> 'Y' then 'true' 
        when arsc.selltype = 'Y' and arsc.holdpercd = '0' then '' 
        when arsc.selltype = 'Y' and arsc.holdpercd in ('1', '2','3','4', '5' )
             and arsc.periodbal[arsc.holdpercd] > 0 then 'true'
else '' end as nosale
JobDefinitionSteps.FromClause: pub.arsc as arsc
JobDefinitionSteps.WhereClause: arsc.cono = {IntegrationConnector_SXeCompany}

JobDefinitionSteps.Name: Refresh ShipTo
JobDefinitionSteps.SelectClause:
arsc.custno as custno,
arss.shipto as shipto,
arsc.custtype as custtype,
arss.name as name,
arss.email as email,
arss.phoneno as phoneno,
ifnull(arss.faxphoneno,'') as faxphoneno,
arss.termstype as termstype,
convert('varchar', arss.pricetype) as pricetype,
arsc.currencyty as currencyty,
arss.whse as whse,
arss.slsrepout as slsrepout,
arss.slsrepin as slsrepin,
ifnull(ifnull(left(convert('varchar', arss.addr), locate(';', convert('varchar', arss.addr)) - 1), left(convert('varchar', arsc.addr), locate(';', convert('varchar', arsc.addr)) - 1)), '') as addr1,
ifnull(ifnull(right(convert('varchar', arss.addr) , length(arss.addr) - locate(';', convert('varchar', arss.addr))), right(convert('varchar', arsc.addr) , length(arsc.addr) - locate(';', convert('varchar', arsc.addr)))), '') as addr2,
'' as addr3,
ifnull(arss.city, arsc.city) as city,
ifnull(arss.state, arsc.state) as state,
case when arss.countrycd = '' then 'US' when arss.countrycd != '' then arss.countrycd end as countrycd,
ifnull(arss.zipcd, arsc.zipcd) as zipcd,     
arss.shipviaty as shipviaty,
case when arss.pdcustno = 0 then '' when arss.pdcustno != 0 then convert('varchar', arss.pdcustno) end as pdcustno,
arsc.bankno as bankno,
case when arss.pricecd = '' then '' 
         when arss.pricecd != '' then convert('varchar',arss.pricecd) end as pricecd,
'' as pdshipto,
convert('varchar',arss.disccd) as disccd,
arss.credlim as credlim,
case arss.statustype
    when 0 then 0
    else case when arss.jobclosedt is null or arss.jobclosedt > CURDATE() then 1 else 0 end  
end as statustype,
arss.poreqfl as porequired,
case when arss.holdpercd = '0' then '' 
        when arss.holdpercd in ('1', '2','3','4', '5' )
             and arss.jobperiodbal[arss.holdpercd] > 0 then 'true'
else '' end as nosale
